&lt;h1 id="making-something-social-destroys-the-truth-of-it"&gt;Making Something Social Destroys the Truth of It&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dec 6 2021&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Science&amp;rsquo;s biggest breakthroughs came from unpopular people&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Naval:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Making something social destroys the truth of it because social groups need consensus to survive—otherwise they fight and can&amp;rsquo;t get along—and consensus is all about compromise, not truth-seeking.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>